Write a Python program to find the sum of the series 2 +22 + 222 + 2222 + .. n terms

Input Format

Line 1:

Constraints

1<=n<=10^7

Output Format

Sample Input 0

5
Sample Output 0

24690
Sample Input 1

7
Sample Output 1

2469134


