Write a Python program to find the sum of the series 2 +22 + 222 + 2222 + .. n terms

Input Format

Line 1:

Constraints

1<=n<=10^7

Output Format

Sample Input 0

5
Sample Output 0

24690
Sample Input 1

7
Sample Output 1

2469134

#include <stdio.h>
#include <string.h>
#include <math.h>
#include <stdlib.h>

int main() {
    int sum=0,n,temp=2,i=1;
    scanf("%d",&n);
    while(i<=n)
    {
        sum=sum+temp;
        temp=temp*10+2;
        i++;

    }
    printf("%d",sum);

    /* Enter your code here. Read input from STDIN. Print output to STDOUT */    
    return 0;
}
